    "collapsible_content_Vr7ChJ": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_content_r9MdDc": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "✅ Will it work on black nails?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely! The built-in LED lights up the quick, letting you see the bloodline clearly every time. Say goodbye to guesswork and nail-cutting accidents—perfect even for dark nails.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_7WhHAK": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "✅ Is it safe for all pet sizes?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! Our trimmer and grinder are designed for pets of every size—small, medium, or large. Multiple port sizes make it easy to groom any dog or cat safely and comfortably.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_kdV9Lf": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "✅ Will this hurt my pet?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Not at all. The blades deliver clean, precise cuts, while the whisper-quiet grinder keeps grooming calm and stress-free. Trim in small amounts and avoid the quick for a completely pain-free experience.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "collapsible_row_content_LBnmdE": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "✅ How often should I trim my pet’s nails?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Most pets do best with trims every 2–4 weeks. Keeping nails healthy and short improves their comfort, paw health, and prevents furniture scratches.<br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
